WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.340
chapter number four.

00:00:01.340 --> 00:00:03.000
And through the summer here,

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:05.880
we have spent Sunday evenings,

00:00:05.880 --> 00:00:07.079
not last Sunday evening,

00:00:07.079 --> 00:00:08.920
but several Sunday evenings.

00:00:08.920 --> 00:00:11.840
We have been studying through a series

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:13.800
that I've entitled Ask the Pastor.

00:00:13.800 --> 00:00:17.159
We gave forms and allowed you to submit questions.

00:00:17.159 --> 00:00:19.239
Originally, we were planning to go through the summer

00:00:19.239 --> 00:00:20.760
with the number of questions submitted.

00:00:20.760 --> 00:00:22.700
We'll go through the fall as well.

00:00:22.700 --> 00:00:24.399
And it'll be a Sunday night series here

00:00:24.399 --> 00:00:25.840
for a number of months.

00:00:25.840 --> 00:00:28.620
And so we're looking forward to it again this evening

00:00:28.700 --> 00:00:30.139
to getting back to the series.

00:00:30.139 --> 00:00:31.940
The question that was asked this evening

00:00:31.940 --> 00:00:33.500
that I'll try to answer

00:00:33.500 --> 00:00:36.159
is where did Cain get his wife?

00:00:36.159 --> 00:00:37.680
And Genesis chapter number four

00:00:37.680 --> 00:00:39.159
is where we'll go this evening

00:00:39.159 --> 00:00:41.259
and begin in that text of scripture

00:00:41.259 --> 00:00:43.060
in order to answer the question.

00:00:43.060 --> 00:00:45.860
And perhaps you've been asked this question

00:00:45.860 --> 00:00:47.580
nearly a hundred years ago now.

00:00:47.580 --> 00:00:50.500
There was a famous trial down in Tennessee,

00:00:50.500 --> 00:00:51.700
the Scopes Trial.

00:00:51.700 --> 00:00:53.759
Many of you might be familiar with that.

00:00:53.759 --> 00:00:55.220
And you've read about it.

00:00:55.220 --> 00:00:57.419
I'm sure that brother Michael has made some study

00:00:57.419 --> 00:00:59.299
perhaps of the Scopes Trial.

00:00:59.299 --> 00:01:00.700
And you see some things there.

00:01:00.700 --> 00:01:01.639
And it's kind of interesting.

00:01:01.639 --> 00:01:05.239
There was an entire line of questioning

00:01:05.239 --> 00:01:07.139
with regard to this very question

00:01:07.139 --> 00:01:08.900
that we're dealing with this evening

00:01:08.900 --> 00:01:11.059
on where Cain got his wife.

00:01:11.059 --> 00:01:12.580
Someone said this,

00:01:12.580 --> 00:01:15.540
that she is the most talked about woman in history,

00:01:15.540 --> 00:01:17.419
though we do not know her name.

00:01:17.419 --> 00:01:20.419
And because of so many folks that have asked the question,

00:01:20.419 --> 00:01:24.180
have sought really to undermine, as I would say it,

00:01:24.180 --> 00:01:26.639
many that are typically asking this question

00:01:26.680 --> 00:01:28.919
are really simply undermining the authority

00:01:28.919 --> 00:01:31.000
and accuracy of scripture.

00:01:31.000 --> 00:01:34.160
And really that's the attack of the enemy, right?

00:01:34.160 --> 00:01:37.199
God has given us his word.

00:01:37.199 --> 00:01:39.440
God wants us to know his word.

00:01:39.440 --> 00:01:42.519
God wants us to believe his word and trust his word.

00:01:42.519 --> 00:01:45.279
But we know that the enemy is constantly trying

00:01:45.279 --> 00:01:47.360
to attack the word of God,

00:01:47.360 --> 00:01:50.000
undermine the authority and the accuracy

00:01:50.000 --> 00:01:50.959
of the word of God.

00:01:50.959 --> 00:01:54.760
And if he can cause there to be a measure of doubt

00:01:54.760 --> 00:01:57.400
in someone's mind and their heart

00:01:57.400 --> 00:02:01.480
with regard to the accuracy of this book,

00:02:01.480 --> 00:02:04.839
he gains really an advantage.

00:02:04.839 --> 00:02:08.559
And we must not allow him to gain an advantage.

00:02:08.559 --> 00:02:11.399
We know that God's word is true.

00:02:11.399 --> 00:02:13.899
Every word of God is pure.

00:02:13.899 --> 00:02:15.440
We know that it's perfect.

00:02:15.440 --> 00:02:17.520
It's been given by inspiration.

00:02:17.520 --> 00:02:19.559
It's been divinely preserved.

00:02:19.559 --> 00:02:22.720
And God has given us everything that we need

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:24.440
right here in the Bible.

00:02:25.119 --> 00:02:26.759
We believe not only the inspiration

00:02:26.759 --> 00:02:28.279
and the preservation of God's word,

00:02:28.279 --> 00:02:30.320
but I believe, and it's so important,

00:02:30.320 --> 00:02:32.160
and maybe something that we don't speak about

00:02:32.160 --> 00:02:35.960
as often enough, but that is the sufficiency of scripture.

00:02:35.960 --> 00:02:37.880
God's word is sufficient.

00:02:37.880 --> 00:02:41.000
God has given us everything that we need to know.

00:02:41.000 --> 00:02:42.839
He's given to us in his word,

00:02:42.839 --> 00:02:44.720
and we're thankful for that.

00:02:44.720 --> 00:02:47.360
Modern day skeptics raise this question,

00:02:47.360 --> 00:02:50.380
and I believe that we ought to be prepared

00:02:50.380 --> 00:02:51.220
to give an answer.

00:02:51.220 --> 00:02:53.240
Notice, if you will, in Genesis 4,

00:02:53.320 --> 00:02:56.520
and this is where they run to, verse 16 and 17,

00:02:56.520 --> 00:02:58.720
of course, after the situation with Cain and Abel

00:02:58.720 --> 00:03:01.039
is recorded in the beginning of Genesis 4,

00:03:01.039 --> 00:03:02.919
and the punishment, if you will,

00:03:02.919 --> 00:03:04.639
that was given out to Cain.

00:03:04.639 --> 00:03:06.279
He, in fact, says that his punishment

00:03:06.279 --> 00:03:07.839
is greater than he can bear.

00:03:07.839 --> 00:03:09.320
But if you notice in verse number 16,

00:03:09.320 --> 00:03:12.039
it says that Cain went out from the presence of the Lord,

00:03:12.039 --> 00:03:13.440
and what a sad statement that is.

00:03:13.440 --> 00:03:17.279
Not really the scope of our study this evening,

00:03:17.279 --> 00:03:18.839
but there's no record whatsoever

00:03:18.839 --> 00:03:22.479
of Cain ever returning to the presence of God.

00:03:22.479 --> 00:03:24.600
And it says that he went out from the presence of the Lord

00:03:24.600 --> 00:03:29.600
and dwelt in the land of Nod on the east of Eden.

00:03:29.720 --> 00:03:32.919
The name of the city where he goes, the land of Nod,

00:03:32.919 --> 00:03:36.919
literally means a land of wandering or exile.

00:03:36.919 --> 00:03:38.919
And then the Bible says this in verse number 17,

00:03:38.919 --> 00:03:43.759
and Cain knew his wife, and she conceived and bare Enoch,

00:03:43.759 --> 00:03:46.759
and he built a city and called the name of the city

00:03:46.759 --> 00:03:49.679
after the name of his son, Enoch.

00:03:49.679 --> 00:03:53.520
Now, as we begin to think about the attack of scripture,

00:03:53.520 --> 00:03:56.800
when these skeptics would ask the question

00:03:56.800 --> 00:03:59.360
and try to undermine, again, the authority

00:03:59.360 --> 00:04:00.839
and the accuracy of the word of God,

00:04:00.839 --> 00:04:04.440
I really believe that the approach that they're taking,

00:04:04.440 --> 00:04:06.000
and if you study what they say

00:04:06.000 --> 00:04:08.440
and the entirety of what they're dealing with,

00:04:08.440 --> 00:04:11.259
what they're trying to cause you to believe

00:04:11.259 --> 00:04:14.720
is that there must have been other human beings created

00:04:14.720 --> 00:04:15.880
other than Adam and Eve.

00:04:15.880 --> 00:04:18.200
It didn't really start with just Adam and Eve.

00:04:18.200 --> 00:04:21.920
And so there's other colonies of people

00:04:21.920 --> 00:04:23.760
that are on the earth.

00:04:23.760 --> 00:04:27.040
And this really becomes a major problem

00:04:27.040 --> 00:04:28.959
when you accept something like that

00:04:28.959 --> 00:04:31.839
because it has a direct correspondence to the gospel,

00:04:31.839 --> 00:04:33.559
and we'll deal with that at the end of the message

00:04:33.559 --> 00:04:36.920
this evening, and do trust it to be a blessing to you.

00:04:36.920 --> 00:04:41.600
But the reality is that they would have us to believe

00:04:41.600 --> 00:04:45.320
that there's no possible way that all of it just started

00:04:45.320 --> 00:04:47.480
with two people, Adam and Eve.

00:04:47.480 --> 00:04:50.160
And this is a really sad situation.

00:04:50.160 --> 00:04:52.140
In fact, I was in the presence of some people

00:04:52.140 --> 00:04:55.760
that I've known for years, and no one from our church,

00:04:55.760 --> 00:04:56.600
but I was in the presence,

00:04:56.600 --> 00:04:58.320
sitting around having conversation.

00:04:58.320 --> 00:05:00.399
And some folks that were at that table

00:05:00.399 --> 00:05:03.799
were folks that grew up in church.

00:05:03.799 --> 00:05:06.000
They'd been in church their whole lives.

00:05:06.000 --> 00:05:07.899
A couple of the folks around the table

00:05:07.899 --> 00:05:10.160
had graduated from Bible college,

00:05:10.160 --> 00:05:12.760
and one of them piped up and they made this statement,

00:05:12.760 --> 00:05:14.519
and actually the individual that made the statement

00:05:14.519 --> 00:05:16.320
was a graduate of Bible college.

00:05:16.320 --> 00:05:17.720
And here's what they said.

00:05:17.720 --> 00:05:19.260
The question that we must really answer

00:05:19.260 --> 00:05:21.220
is how many Adams were there?

00:05:23.480 --> 00:05:26.059
And really what was happening in that individual's life

00:05:26.059 --> 00:05:30.760
is they were just buying into the false teaching,

00:05:30.760 --> 00:05:33.959
the undermining of the authority of Scripture,

00:05:33.959 --> 00:05:36.040
and believing that, well, yeah, I mean,

00:05:36.040 --> 00:05:37.799
Cain had to get away from somewhere,

00:05:37.799 --> 00:05:40.239
and so, yeah, I guess it kind of makes sense

00:05:40.239 --> 00:05:42.279
that there were other groups of people.

00:05:42.279 --> 00:05:43.600
You know, just go back to the Bible

00:05:43.600 --> 00:05:45.420
and read what God's word says,

00:05:45.459 --> 00:05:48.140
and trust what God's word says,

00:05:48.140 --> 00:05:52.459
and God will help us to have the discernment that we need.

00:05:52.459 --> 00:05:55.140
And so as we think about the question that is raised,

00:05:55.140 --> 00:05:59.299
and they begin to approach it with regard to Cain's wife,

00:05:59.299 --> 00:06:00.980
again, I believe that it's dangerous

00:06:00.980 --> 00:06:03.559
because of the impact on the gospel,

00:06:03.559 --> 00:06:06.440
the direct correlation throughout the word of God

00:06:06.440 --> 00:06:10.540
with regard to the fall of man, the sin nature of man,

00:06:10.540 --> 00:06:12.119
it all going back to Adam,

00:06:12.119 --> 00:06:14.100
and of course Eve being in transgression.

00:06:14.100 --> 00:06:16.540
You look at the New Testament

00:06:16.540 --> 00:06:18.619
and the references to Adam and Eve.

00:06:18.619 --> 00:06:21.459
And so tonight, I hope that through answering the question,

00:06:21.459 --> 00:06:23.100
very simply, we can answer the question,

00:06:23.100 --> 00:06:24.500
where did Cain get his wife?

00:06:24.500 --> 00:06:26.299
But I hope this evening that I could prove to you

00:06:26.299 --> 00:06:29.779
some additional things with regard to really helping us

00:06:29.779 --> 00:06:31.700
to be able to have ourselves settled

00:06:31.700 --> 00:06:33.619
and grounded in the faith.

00:06:33.619 --> 00:06:35.779
And really, that's the objective.

00:06:35.779 --> 00:06:38.100
We understand the great commission

00:06:38.100 --> 00:06:40.299
that's been given to us as a local church,

00:06:40.299 --> 00:06:41.899
as New Testament believers.

00:06:41.899 --> 00:06:43.220
We've been given the commission

00:06:43.220 --> 00:06:45.700
to go out and preach the gospel to every creature,

00:06:45.700 --> 00:06:47.619
baptizing them in the name of the Father,

00:06:47.619 --> 00:06:48.619
the Son, and the Holy Ghost,

00:06:48.619 --> 00:06:52.119
and then teaching them to observe all things

00:06:52.119 --> 00:06:54.339
whatsoever I have commanded you.

00:06:54.339 --> 00:06:58.100
And that process of discipleship is so imperative

00:06:58.100 --> 00:07:00.220
that the people of God would be settled

00:07:00.220 --> 00:07:01.739
and grounded in the faith,

00:07:01.739 --> 00:07:04.140
that we would not have some skeptic,

00:07:04.140 --> 00:07:07.760
some individual that's just seeking to undermine

00:07:07.760 --> 00:07:09.700
the authority and the accuracy of scripture

00:07:09.700 --> 00:07:10.940
that would come to us and say,

00:07:10.940 --> 00:07:13.380
oh yeah, well, tell me about where Cain got his wife.

00:07:13.380 --> 00:07:14.220
And then all of a sudden,

00:07:14.220 --> 00:07:17.299
everything that we've believed just kind of falls apart

00:07:17.299 --> 00:07:20.380
because we're not settled, we're not grounded.

00:07:20.380 --> 00:07:25.059
We do not have the ability to give the answer

00:07:25.059 --> 00:07:27.019
of the hope that lieth within us.

00:07:27.019 --> 00:07:29.700
And our goal, our objective,

00:07:29.700 --> 00:07:32.799
is not only to evangelize the world,

00:07:32.799 --> 00:07:34.820
but to edify the believer.

00:07:34.820 --> 00:07:38.299
That word edify was a word that was used very commonly

00:07:38.299 --> 00:07:41.700
with regard to building and construction.

00:07:41.700 --> 00:07:45.619
It means to build up and that we would be settled

00:07:45.619 --> 00:07:47.380
and grounded in the faith.

00:07:47.380 --> 00:07:50.140
And so a few statements this evening

00:07:50.140 --> 00:07:52.420
as we go through the message.

00:07:52.420 --> 00:07:53.779
Number one, I would say this,

00:07:53.779 --> 00:07:55.459
the scriptures clearly teach us

00:07:55.459 --> 00:07:59.619
that God created Adam and Eve to start the human race.

00:07:59.619 --> 00:08:02.940
There's no other areas of scripture

00:08:02.940 --> 00:08:04.660
where there would be any indication,

00:08:04.660 --> 00:08:07.660
not even the slightest indication

00:08:07.660 --> 00:08:10.660
of any other human beings being created.

00:08:10.660 --> 00:08:15.339
In fact, the scriptures make it abundantly clear

00:08:15.339 --> 00:08:16.980
that it was only Adam and Eve.

00:08:16.980 --> 00:08:20.179
Look in Genesis one in verse number 26 through 28

00:08:20.179 --> 00:08:22.440
and verses that we're familiar with,

00:08:22.440 --> 00:08:23.899
but notice what the Bible says.

00:08:23.899 --> 00:08:26.059
And God said in verse 26,

00:08:26.059 --> 00:08:30.179
let us make man in our image after our likeness

00:08:30.179 --> 00:08:33.460
and let them have dominion over the fish of the sea

00:08:33.460 --> 00:08:35.539
and over the fowl of the air and over the cattle

00:08:35.539 --> 00:08:37.900
and over all the earth and over every creeping thing

00:08:37.900 --> 00:08:40.799
that creepeth upon the earth, verse 27.

00:08:40.799 --> 00:08:43.299
So God created man in his own image

00:08:43.299 --> 00:08:45.640
and the image of God created he him,

00:08:45.640 --> 00:08:48.299
male and female created he them

00:08:48.299 --> 00:08:51.780
and God blessed them and God said unto them,

00:08:51.780 --> 00:08:55.659
be fruitful and multiply and replenish the earth

00:08:55.659 --> 00:08:58.900
and subdue it and have dominion over the fish of the sea

00:08:58.900 --> 00:09:00.219
and over the fowl of the air

00:09:00.219 --> 00:09:03.099
and over every living thing that moveth

00:09:03.739 --> 00:09:04.580
upon the earth.

00:09:04.580 --> 00:09:08.580
And we see the record on day six where God created mankind.

00:09:08.580 --> 00:09:11.619
Of course, God gives us further insight

00:09:11.619 --> 00:09:14.260
in chapter number two with regard to some details

00:09:14.260 --> 00:09:15.659
and we'll look at that here in just a moment,

00:09:15.659 --> 00:09:18.460
but I do wanna make you aware of,

00:09:18.460 --> 00:09:21.359
and you already are, but just to be mindful this evening,

00:09:21.359 --> 00:09:23.580
that in verse 28, God said to them,

00:09:23.580 --> 00:09:26.340
be fruitful and multiply.

00:09:26.340 --> 00:09:28.580
This was a command that was given to Adam and Eve.

00:09:28.580 --> 00:09:30.659
We also find it's a command that's given to Noah,

00:09:30.659 --> 00:09:34.940
his wife, his sons, and their wives after the flood

00:09:34.940 --> 00:09:38.780
and I believe that they did fulfill and God blessed.

00:09:38.780 --> 00:09:41.059
See, God is the giver of life

00:09:41.059 --> 00:09:44.479
and God allowed them to multiply,

00:09:44.479 --> 00:09:47.940
to be able to fulfill the command that he had given.

00:09:47.940 --> 00:09:52.260
Of course, the ability to have perhaps multiple children

00:09:53.179 --> 00:09:56.260
at one time with regard to twins or triplets

00:09:56.260 --> 00:09:59.340
and so on and so forth and God was blessing

00:09:59.340 --> 00:10:00.179
as he had given.

00:10:00.179 --> 00:10:01.779
in them this command.

00:10:01.779 --> 00:10:04.259
But I want you to notice in chapter number two,

00:10:04.259 --> 00:10:06.379
and I'm gonna read a number of verses in chapter number two,

00:10:06.379 --> 00:10:08.819
and I want you to notice as we read these verses

00:10:08.819 --> 00:10:13.619
of scripture how that God always speaks in the singular

00:10:14.459 --> 00:10:16.679
with regard to creation of man.

00:10:16.679 --> 00:10:18.099
Notice in verse number five,

00:10:18.099 --> 00:10:21.699
in every plant of the field before it was in the earth,

00:10:21.699 --> 00:10:23.359
in every herb of the field before it grew,

00:10:23.359 --> 00:10:26.179
for the Lord God had not caused its rain upon the earth,

00:10:26.179 --> 00:10:31.179
and there was not a man to till the ground.

00:10:33.059 --> 00:10:34.979
It's pretty straightforward, is it not?

00:10:34.979 --> 00:10:36.859
God's not saying there wasn't a man here.

00:10:36.859 --> 00:10:38.279
There's not a man.

00:10:38.279 --> 00:10:40.419
So it's not that there were other people

00:10:40.419 --> 00:10:41.859
that were created somewhere else

00:10:41.859 --> 00:10:44.739
that Cain is able to travel to Nod

00:10:44.739 --> 00:10:48.299
and find a group of people there, no.

00:10:48.299 --> 00:10:52.339
The Bible says that there was not a man to till the ground.

00:10:52.339 --> 00:10:54.059
Notice in verse number eight,

00:10:54.099 --> 00:10:58.019
it says in the Lord God planted a garden eastward in Eden,

00:10:58.019 --> 00:11:03.019
and there he put the man whom he had formed.

00:11:03.019 --> 00:11:07.179
It's Adam, singular, the man that he had formed.

00:11:07.179 --> 00:11:08.939
You see in verse number 15,

00:11:08.939 --> 00:11:11.659
the Bible says in the Lord God took the man

00:11:11.659 --> 00:11:13.939
and put him into the garden of Eden

00:11:13.939 --> 00:11:15.779
to dress it and to keep it,

00:11:15.779 --> 00:11:18.779
and the Lord God commanded the man,

00:11:18.779 --> 00:11:23.019
saying, of every tree of the garden thou mayest freely eat,

00:11:23.019 --> 00:11:25.059
but of the tree of the knowledge of good and evil,

00:11:25.059 --> 00:11:26.579
thou shalt not eat of it,

00:11:26.579 --> 00:11:28.499
for in the day that thou eatest thereof,

00:11:28.499 --> 00:11:31.639
thou shalt surely die.

00:11:31.639 --> 00:11:34.659
In verse number 18, it says the Lord God said it is not good

00:11:34.659 --> 00:11:37.459
that the man should be alone.

00:11:37.459 --> 00:11:38.939
So what's God gonna do?

00:11:38.939 --> 00:11:43.059
I will make him and help me for him.

00:11:43.059 --> 00:11:45.339
Amen, verse 19, and out of the ground,

00:11:45.339 --> 00:11:47.699
the Lord God formed every beast of the field

00:11:47.699 --> 00:11:49.879
and every fowl of the air and brought them unto Adam

00:11:49.879 --> 00:11:51.839
to see what he would call them

00:11:51.839 --> 00:11:54.079
and what sort of Adam called every living creature,

00:11:54.079 --> 00:11:55.439
that was the name thereof,

00:11:55.439 --> 00:11:57.679
and Adam gave names to all cattle,

00:11:57.679 --> 00:11:59.759
to all, and to the fowl of the air,

00:11:59.759 --> 00:12:01.479
and to every beast of the field,

00:12:01.479 --> 00:12:06.479
but for Adam there was not found in help meat for him.

00:12:08.139 --> 00:12:10.239
If God had created other peoples

00:12:10.239 --> 00:12:12.039
in other places of the earth,

