help us to be encouraged as we've studied your word.

00:44:42.200 --> 00:44:44.400
We thank you for giving us your word,

00:44:44.400 --> 00:44:45.400
and we just pray that you'd bless

00:44:45.400 --> 00:44:46.800
the remainder of our evening.

00:44:46.800 --> 00:44:47.800
We'll thank you for it.

00:44:47.800 --> 00:44:48.800
In Christ's name we pray.

00:44:48.800 --> 00:44:49.800
Would you stand with me?

00:44:49.800 --> 00:44:51.400
Heads are bowed, eyes are closed.

00:44:51.400 --> 00:44:54.000
Give an opportunity for a invitation this evening.

00:44:54.000 --> 00:44:56.200
Maybe just wanna come and thank God for his word.

00:44:56.200 --> 00:44:59.400
And just so thankful that God's given us the Bible,

00:44:59.400 --> 00:45:02.000
and that the Bible has the answers,

00:45:02.000 --> 00:45:04.000
and maybe God spoke to your heart

00:45:04.000 --> 00:45:05.400
through some other way throughout the day.

00:45:05.400 --> 00:45:07.600
The altar is open as Kimberly plays.

00:45:07.600 --> 00:45:08.800
Thank you.

